      <h3>Naturelo: Purpose-Built Iron for Plant-Based Diets</h3>

      <p>Naturelo designs supplements specifically for people following plant-based lifestyles, and their Vegan Iron Gummies reflect that focus. Every ingredient is plant-derived — the iron comes from organic whole food sources, the vitamin C from acerola cherry, and the gummy base uses pectin rather than animal-derived gelatin. For vegans who are already aware that their dietary iron (non-heme) is 2 to 3 times less bioavailable than animal-sourced heme iron, a dedicated vegan iron supplement is not optional — it is essential.</p>

      <p>The organic vitamin C from acerola cherry is a thoughtful addition. Acerola is one of the richest natural sources of vitamin C, and research published in <em>The Journal of Nutrition</em> has shown that natural vitamin C complexes from whole food sources may enhance mineral absorption more effectively than synthetic ascorbic acid alone. The added folate supports DNA synthesis during red blood cell formation — a common co-deficiency in vegan populations.</p>

